{"tid":1071872,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"政府統計處 訪問員 2019","createTime":"2019-03-21T15:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T02:29:55.000Z","uid":57985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"01b751abbdbe2e7ffe0569b88ce531f46ad980af","tid":1071872,"uid":57985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人apply左做訪問員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部門:\t政府統計處 <br />\n組別/單位:\t物價統計科及社會統計科 <br />\n職位名稱:\t訪問員 <br />\n薪酬:\t每月港幣17, 855元 <br />\n入職條件:\t申請人必須&ndash; <br />\n(a) (i) 在香港中學文憑考試五科考獲第2級或同等(註1) 或以上成績(註2)，或具同等學歷；或 (ii) 在香港中學會考五科考獲第2級(註3) ╱E 級或以上成績(註2)，或具同等學歷；及 <br />\n(b) 符合語文能力要求，即在香港中學文憑考試或香港中學會考中國語文科和英國語文科考獲第2級(註3) 或以上成績，或具同等成績；及 <br />\n(c) 能閱讀及書寫中文及英文；以及 <br />\n(d) 操流利粵語、普通話及英語。"},{"pid":"7287512ce915d89f5d769c2b2974f8507612cfa0","tid":1071872,"uid":111520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"Apply jor 留名"},{"pid":"cb4805ab9dca1a2d8f4dc0204bc872a96113d0b4","tid":1071872,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f679eb2825732d5cfb9a127e7a6beae049e726","tid":1071872,"uid":57985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4805ab9dca1a2d8f4dc0204bc872a96113d0b4","tid":1071872,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed810813fd3470c571fd57adbaf3a041d21ba75","tid":1071872,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f679eb2825732d5cfb9a127e7a6beae049e726","tid":1071872,"uid":57985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4